      "writtenOn": "2020-10-01T14:33:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "They can\u0027t any longer. (At least until I get further in this refactor and rearrange how we look them up). The problem is that we\u0027re putting the program elements into a map, indexed by variable name, so we\u0027d have a many-to-one thing (and cloning the element would pull in all of those variables, even if we only used one). I think we can fix this in a future CL, but this was the easiest solution for now, given that we only ever declare things one-at-a-time.",
